name: Alea Iacta Est Software Development
body:
### About Us ###

[Alea Iacta Est](https://portal.aie-guild.org/) (AIE) is a online gaming community for players of massively multiplayer online role-playing games (MMORPGs).  Our community is built upon the belief that respect and courtesy for fellow gamers is fundamental to a worthwhile gaming experience.

This site is the hub of all software development within the AIE community.
